<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17271] PerReplicaState: Shard leader elections still impact state.json</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17271</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From testing it has been found that shard leader elections when there are multiple replicas still touches state.json, even when PerReplicaState (PRS) is enabled. With PRS, leader should be contained in the per replica state so we should not have to modify state.json.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
